</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 8:05
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='474000' id='t-474000'>Why would you willingly expose yourself to bad news?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='477000' id='t-477000'>Okay, you simply wouldn't.</span>
