<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='620000' id='t-620000'>And I'd be wrong to dis that completely.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='623000' id='t-623000'>Moving over, we come, of course, to consultancy.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
10:36
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='625000' id='t-625000'>(Laughter)</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
10:40
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='629000' id='t-629000'>I thought it was very indecent of Accenture</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='631000' id='t-631000'>to ditch Tiger Woods in such</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='633000' id='t-633000'>a sort of hurried and hasty way.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='635000' id='t-635000'>I mean, Tiger surely was actually obeying the Accenture model.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='638000' id='t-638000'>He developed an interesting outsourcing model for sexual services,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='641000' id='t-641000'>(Laughter)</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='643000' id='t-643000'>no longer tied to a single monopoly provider,</span>
