<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
11:09
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='658000' id='t-658000'>Then there are other things that don't cost much and achieve absolutely nothing.</span>
