<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='682000' id='t-682000'>to their expense, their efforts</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='684000' id='t-684000'>and the disruption they cause.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
11:37
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='686000' id='t-686000'>So the first thing I'd like</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='688000' id='t-688000'>is a competition -- to anybody watching this as a film --</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='690000' id='t-690000'>is to come up with a name for that stuff on the bottom right.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='693000' id='t-693000'>And the second thing, I think,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='695000' id='t-695000'>is that the world needs to have people in charge of that.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='697000' id='t-697000'>That's why I call for the &quot;Chief Detail Officer.&quot;</span>
