<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='704000' id='t-704000'>The people who actually have no money,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='706000' id='t-706000'>who have no extravagant budget,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='708000' id='t-708000'>but who realize that actually</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='710000' id='t-710000'>you might achieve greater success in uptake</span>
