<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='723000' id='t-723000'>And if actually we created a Ministry of Detail</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='726000' id='t-726000'>and business actually had Chief Detail Officers,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='728000' id='t-728000'>then that fourth quadrant,</span>
